dsDescriptionValue.value: Information seeking behavior among PhD-students is very interesting to the research libraries, since this sub-group of researchers represent the researchers of the future and the habits they acquire now they will carry on. Therefor it is important that the libraries know this group of patrons in order to best service them.

value: The survey covers PhD-students fro the universities of Copenhagen, Oslo and Vienna.
